text: Kaysersberg is a former commune. It is found in the Haut-Rhin department of eastern France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Kaysersberg-Vignoble.Arrêté 14 July 2015 == References == Category:Former communes in Haut-Rhin Category:2016 disestablishments in France
title: Kaysersberg
